%html
  %head
    %meta{:content => "text/html; charset=utf-8", "http-equiv" => "Content-Type"}
      %title YesTrak - Welcome
      :css
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        body, html {
            background: #f2f2f2;
            font: normal 14px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }
    %body
    %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "background:#f2f2f2; text-align:center;", :width => "100%"}
      %tr
        %td{:align => "center"}
          %table{:align => "center", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :width => "100%"}
            = render partial: 'mailer_partials/email_header'
            %tr
              %td{:align => "center"}
                %table{:align => "center", :border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :style => "width:800px; margin:0 auto;"}
                  %tr
                    %td{:style => "height:45px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"}
                  %tr
                    %td{:style => "background:#ffffff; text-align:center;"}
                      %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :width => "100%"}
                        %tr
                          %td{:colspan => "5", :style => "height:30px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"}
                        %tr
                          %td{:style => "width:27px;"}
                          %td{:style => "width:70px; vertical-align:top;"}
                            %img{:alt => "", :src => "#{APP_CONFIG['image_url']}icon_09.png", :width => "70"}/
                          %td{:style => "width:32px;"}
                          %td{:style => "width:644px; vertical-align:top; text-align:left;"}
                            %table{:border => "0", :cellpadding => "0", :cellspacing => "0", :width => "100%"}
                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "font:normal 25px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#21afd7; text-transform:uppercase;"} A New script has been created
                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "font:italic 14px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#a1c53e;"}= @created_at.in_time_zone(@phone_script.tenant.timezone).strftime("%B %d, %Y at %l:%M%P")
                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "height:27px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "font:normal 15px/30px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                  A script name
                                  %span{style: 'font-weight: bold;'}
                                    #{@script_name}
                                  has been created.

                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "height:27px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#21afd7; text-transform:uppercase; font-weight:bold;"} Script:
                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "font:normal 14px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#a1c53e; text-transform:uppercase;"}= PhoneScript::SCRIPT_ID[@script_id]
                              %tr
                                %td{:style => "height:27px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;

                              - if @script_id == 'take_msg'
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    My name is William, how may I help you today?
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    I'm part of the answering team for #{@phone_script.buss_name}. #{@phone_script.not_available_excuse}. My job is to take a message #{@phone_script.desired_action}.
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    May I please start with your phone number in case we get disconnected? Great. May I please have your first name? Thank you. May I please have your last name? Thanks, Now that we have your contact info, what's the message you'd like me to take? Great. One last question: what is the best time to reach you by phone?
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    Thanks, I'll send your answers through now #{@phone_script.next_step}. My name is William, and it's been a pleasure assisting you. Is there anything else we can do for you today?
                              - elsif @script_id == 'book_apt'
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    My name is William, how may I help you today?
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    I'm part of the answering team for #{@phone_script.buss_name}. My job is to get some quick information from you so we can get you scheduled for #{@phone_script.appointment_type}.
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    May I please start with your phone number in case we get disconnected? Great. May I please have your first name? Thank you. May I please have your last name? Thanks. Now that we have your contact info, what day were you looking to schedule?
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    Question 1: #{@phone_script.try(:question_1)}
                                    %br
                                    Question 2: #{@phone_script.try(:question_2)}
                                    %br
                                    Question 3: #{@phone_script.try(:question_3)}
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    Great – thanks for your help. #{@phone_script.next_step}. My name is William, and it’s been a pleasure assisting you. Is there anything else we can do for you today?
                              - elsif @script_id == 'gather_info'
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    My name is William, how may I help you today?
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    I'm part of the answering team for #{@phone_script.buss_name}. My job is to get some quick information from you so #{@phone_script.desired_action}.
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    May I please start with your phone number in case we get disconnected? Great. May I please have your first name? Thank you. May I please have your last name?
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    Thanks, Now that we have your contact info, let me ask you a few questions: #{@phone_script.question_1}, #{@phone_script.question_2}, #{@phone_script.question_3}. Great. One last question: what is the best time to reach you by phone?
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "height:15px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"} &nbsp;
                                %tr
                                  %td{:style => "font:normal 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#1e1e1f;"}
                                    Thanks for providing us with this information, I'll send your answers through now, and you can expect #{@phone_script.next_step}. My name is William, and it's been a pleasure assisting you. Is there anything else we can do for you today?

                              = render partial: 'mailer_partials/dotted_line'
                              = render partial: 'mailer_partials/tag_line'
                              = render partial: 'mailer_partials/social_links'
                          %td{:style => "width:27px;"}
                        %tr
                          %td{:colspan => "5", :style => "height:30px; line-height:0; font-size:0;"}
                  = render partial: 'mailer_partials/unsubscribe_line'